<item>
            <title>[LU-5571] Test failure sanity-lfsck test_13: (2) unexpected status</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5571</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Nathaniel Clark &amp;lt;nathaniel.l.clark@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/c07fa6c6-189a-11e4-bd79-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/c07fa6c6-189a-11e4-bd79-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/fe33929a-2fe0-11e4-957a-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/fe33929a-2fe0-11e4-957a-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/fe22e280-3146-11e4-b503-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/fe22e280-3146-11e4-b503-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/199c6a08-31d9-11e4-a833-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/199c6a08-31d9-11e4-a833-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_13 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(2) unexpected status&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity-lfsck 13&lt;/p&gt;</description>
